title: La Naturaleza
description: Healthfood shop offering herbal remedies, supplements, dry foods including a big range of gluten-free and celiac- friendly food. Also fresh baked goods, tofu, veggie-burgers, yoghurts, snack bars, and toiletries. Will take orders. Acupuncture sessions are also available as well as a personalized diet service.
streetAddress: Calle Alcalde Antonio Garcia, 3, Arroyo de la Miel, Malaga
